              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-262-WILH-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">ANOTHER,&#13;</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-262-WILH-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-262-WILH-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-262-WILH-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1">By the SAME.</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-262-WILH-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-262-WILH-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-262-WILH-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-262-WILH-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">A</hi> Bard, on whom <hi rend="italics">Phœbus</hi> his Spirit bestow'd,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-WILH-line-2" n="2">Resolv'd to acknowledge the Bounty he ow'd;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-WILH-line-3" n="3">Found out a new Method at once of confessing,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-WILH-line-4" n="4">And making the most of so mighty a Blessing:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-WILH-line-5" n="5">To the God he'd be grateful, but Mortals he'd chouse.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-WILH-line-6" n="6">By making his Patron preside in his House;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-WILH-line-7" n="7">And wisely foresaw this Advantage from thence,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-WILH-line-8" n="8">That the God must in Honour bear most of th' Expence:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-WILH-line-9" n="9">So the Bard he finds Drink, and leaves <hi rend="italics">Phœbus</hi> to treat</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-WILH-line-10" n="10">With the Thoughts he inspires, regardless of Meat:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-WILH-line-11" n="11">Hence they that come hither, expecting to dine,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-WILH-line-12" n="12">Are always fob'd off, with Sheer-Wit, and Sheer-Wine.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
